? ESOL [9] contains water solubility data (log solubility in mols per liter) for common organic 
small molecules. It is a standard dataset that is widely used to estimate solubility directly. 
? FreeSolv [34] contains the experimental values of free energy of hydration of small 
molecules in water. The values are all obtained through molecular dynamics simulations. 
? Lipophilicity [15] is collected from the ChEMBL database [15], containing the experi-
